cs.SE, cs.SY, cs.AI, cs.SD, cs.PL 

This paper discusses the development of software construction paradigms inspired by the laws of organization and development of ecosystems. This topic falls under the category of software engineering (cs.SE) and systems and control (cs.SY). Additionally, the paper mentions the use of artificial intelligence (cs.AI) and programming languages (cs.PL) in the development of these paradigms. Finally, the paper discusses the dynamic nature of ecosystems, which could also fall under the category of software development (cs.SD).
